N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 455.54 - Public restaurant

State Regulations

This functional reporting center must contain all the
expenses associated with the operation of a restaurant open to the general
public on the premises of the residential health care facility. (a) Standard unit of measure. None. (b) Data source. Not applicable. Notes
